    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>再来一盘</i>！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款基于物理的欢乐游戏中，你将用各种奇怪的盘子来上菜——比如香肠，乒乓球拍和大师剑。保持平衡，把菜送到顾客嘴里，优秀的服务将为你解锁新的奇怪盘子，啊哈，再来一盘！</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于物理的玩法</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种关卡和盘子</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持单人游玩和双人协作</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自定义长相和装扮（开发中）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对应盘子的迷你游戏（开发中）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >派对模式、对战模式（开发中）</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想要增加新的盘子，或者有其他建议？快在评论区告诉我们吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305190/extras/0d583d1a2af830b5dc9f6c9b48217df4.avif?t=1771255134\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305190/extras_big/0d583d1a2af830b5dc9f6c9b48217df4.avif?t=1771255134 width=800 height=314 /></span></p>",
